com.googlecode.gwtmvc.client.place
Class DivWrapperPlacer

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.gwtmvc.client.place.DivWrapperPlacer
All Implemented Interfaces:
DomPlacer
public class DivWrapperPlacer
extends Object
implements DomPlacer

A DivWrapperPlacer is a DomPlacer based on the initial html file.
This html file must contain some div with unique id.
The html file acts as a decorator. It first place all static content, then different views are placed in the page.
